Hi all 😊 My name is Koeto Eto and this is my channel about various entertaining and funny videos related to such popular characters as Dame Tu Cosita, Patila, Crazy Frog, Gummy Bear and other equally popular characters.

My channel (Koeto Eto) can even claim to be a teaching channel. After all, each of my videos is built in such a way as to develop mindfulness and observation.

Over time, there will be more and more videos on the channel, and you definitely won’t be able to get bored here 🥳
